parameters: I obtained the explosive laughter mushroom!

\nw[Kuno]Judging from the name, it sounds suspicious... I
wonder if it's safe.

\nw[Nonna]There might be a cooking method that can remove
the poison.

\nw[Nonna]Just because there are a lot of them, doesn't mean
you should eat them, okay? It can be dangerous if
the poison spreads.

\nw[Taro]I'll give you something proper to eat later, so
please behave for now.
\nw[Taro]Well then, I guess I'll head home for today.
